The paper discusses distance metric learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision. The focus on promoting balancedness, compactness, and generalization suggests that the paper is likely to be in the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). However, the use of datasets and experiments suggests that it could also be in the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or multimedia (cs.MM).
